    "The router uses your identity master key as your billing account. Create or restore an identity before adding credits or calling Osaurus models." : {
      "comment" : "A description under the \"Set up your Osaurus Identity\" label, explaining the purpose of the identity master key.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "The router uses your identity master key as your billing account. Create or restore an identity before adding credits or calling Osaurus models."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "路由器将您的身份主密钥用作您的计费账户。在添加积分或调用Osaurus模型之前，请创建或恢复身份。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The sandbox image and Containerization runtime are supported on Apple Silicon." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Das Sandbox-Image und die Containerization-Laufzeit werden auf Apple Silicon unterstützt."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Apple 硅芯片支持沙盒映像和容器化运行时。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The sandbox requires macOS 26 or later; this host reports macOS %lld." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Die Sandbox benötigt macOS 26 oder höher; dieser Host meldet macOS %lld."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "沙盒需要 macOS 26 或更高版本；此主机报告 macOS %lld。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The saved key is injected using the provider-specific header." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Der gespeicherte Schluessel wird mit dem anbieterspezifischen Header eingefuegt."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "保存的密钥使用特定于提供商的标头注入。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The setupComplete flag is false, so tool and agent startup still require provisioning." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Das SetupComplete-Flag ist falsch, daher müssen Tool- und Agent-Start immer noch bereitgestellt werden."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "设置完成标志为false，因此工具和智能体启动仍需要配置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The signing key for \"%@\" has changed. Uninstall the plugin and reinstall it to accept the new key." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Der Signaturschlüssel für \"%@\" hat sich geändert. Deinstallieren Sie das Plugin und installieren Sie es neu, um den neuen Schlüssel zu akzeptieren."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“%@”的签名密钥已更改。卸载插件并重新安装以接受新密钥。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The stdio provider is missing a command." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "The stdio provider is missing a command."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "stdio 提供者缺少一个命令。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The storage encryption key is unavailable on this Mac (Keychain reset, app re-sign, or migration without iCloud Keychain). Your encrypted memory can't be unlocked with the current key." : {
      "comment" : "Detailed explanation of why the memory database can't be unlocked.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Der Speicherverschlüsselungsschlüssel ist auf diesem Mac nicht verfügbar (Schlüsselbund zurücksetzen, App neu signieren oder Migration ohne iCloud-Schlüsselbund). Ihre verschlüsselte Speicher kann mit dem aktuellen Schlüssel nicht entsperrt werden."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此Mac上的存储加密密钥不可用（钥匙串重置、应用程序重新签名或未使用iCloud钥匙串进行迁移）。无法使用当前密钥解密您的加密内存。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The task is still running. Dismissing will cancel it." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Die Aufgabe läuft noch. Schließen bricht sie ab."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "任务仍在运行中。取消将终止它。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Test button launches the subprocess, runs initialize/listTools, and tears it down." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Die Schaltflaeche Test startet den Teilprozess, fuehrt initialize/listTools aus und beendet ihn."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "测试按钮启动子进程，运行initialize/listTools，并将其关闭。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The token or secret header is stored outside plain provider config." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Das Token oder der geheime Header wird ausserhalb der einfachen Anbieterkonfiguration gespeichert."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "令牌或密钥头存储在明文提供者配置之外。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The unreadable database is moved to ~/.osaurus/quarantine/ (never deleted) and a fresh, empty memory store is created so memory and search work again. Distilled facts and episodes in the old file stay in quarantine — export a plaintext backup first if you might recover the key." : {
      "comment" : "Alert message in the \"Reset store\" alert, explaining the purpose of the reset action.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Die unlesbare Datenbank wird nach ~/.osaurus/quarantine/ verschoben (nie gelöscht) und ein neuer, leerer Speicherspeicher wird erstellt, damit Speicher und Suche wieder funktionieren. Destillierte Fakten und Episoden in der alten Datei bleiben in Quarantäne - exportieren Sie zuerst ein Klartext-Backup, wenn Sie den Schlüssel wiederherstellen können."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "无法读取的数据库已被移动到 ~/.osaurus/quarantine/ 目录（不会被删除），并创建了一个全新的空内存存储，以便记忆和搜索功能再次正常工作。旧文件中的提炼事实和情节保留在隔离区——如果您可能需要恢复密钥，请先导出纯文本备份。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The work task is still running. Dismissing will cancel the task." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Die Arbeitsaufgabe läuft noch. Das Beenden wird die Aufgabe abbrechen."
