            "value" : "这些服务器附带的是占位凭据。点击其中一个以打开其编辑器并粘贴真实令牌："
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These settings apply to all voice modes: Voice Input, Transcription, and VAD Mode." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese Einstellungen gelten für alle Sprachmodi: Spracheingabe, Transkription und VAD-Modus."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
